question:
defined on the integers that satisfies the following conditions.
\begin{itemize}
\item[(i)] $f(f(n)) = n$, for all integers $n$;
\item[(ii)] $f(f(n+2)+2) = n$ for all integers $n$;
\item[(iii)] $f(0) = 1$.
\end{itemize}

