kernel_variant.question:
Let   f : \mathbb{Z} \to  \mathbb{Z}   be a function that fulfils
(i)  f(f(n)) = n                for every n \in  \mathbb{Z};
(ii) f( f(n+5) + 5 ) = n        for every n \in  \mathbb{Z};
(iii) f(0) = 7.
Determine all such functions f.
